      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张子显上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00002",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "十载寒窗苦，但愿早成名。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00003",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "在下张子显。我父在朝，官居武陵侯之职。今乃大比之年，上京赶考。打此经过，又被一打虎壮士，劫进他府。适才有一位年老妈妈，在我面前提起亲事。是那妈妈临行言道，少时有人送灯前来。这件事，倒叫我难猜难解也。",
      "text_length": 99
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00004",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "老妈妈作此事太以短见，她言道有一女要配夫选。又言道少时间有人来到，这件事倒叫我难以解开。将身儿坐至在书馆以内，看一看是何人送灯前来？",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00005",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "内西皮导板",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "有桂娟持银灯怎敢怠慢？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00006",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "桂娟上，老妇上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00007",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "绣阁里来了我女儿桂娟。明亮亮银灯儿照粉面，一阵阵迎风过丹墀。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00008",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "急急地走来掉金钗，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00009",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "且住。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00010",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "儿为何不走？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00011",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "妈妈，儿头上金钗掉了。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00012",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "妈妈与儿拾起，与儿插上。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00013",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "是。走吓。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00014",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "罗裙下失掉了红绣花鞋。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00015",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "儿吓，为何又不走了？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00016",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "妈妈，儿的花鞋掉了。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00017",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "为娘与你拔上。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00018",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "走吓。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00019",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "行走来在书馆外，羞答答怎见那秀才？",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00020",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "桂娟站住。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00021",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "走吓。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00022",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "儿不走了。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00023",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "儿为何不走？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00024",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "儿怕。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00025",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "怕什么？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00026",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "儿怕害羞。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00027",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "儿附耳上来，去也在你，不去也在你。为娘要回上房去了。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00028",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "老妇下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00029",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "叫头",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "妈妈，娘吓！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00030",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "有桂娟只生得命运低，未出绣阁愁满怀。来在了书馆用目观看，",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00031",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "呀！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00032",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "桌案上睡下了一少年。我将这银灯放桌面，他问我一声答一言。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00033",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "书馆里闷坏我张子显，",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00034",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "桂娟咳嗽。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00035",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "倒叫子显着了忙。若不然上前去拿礼见，",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00036",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "吓！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00037",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "书馆内来了女天仙。搬椅儿，把桌案，打扫尘土好几番。小娘子请到书馆里面坐，有劳你送灯到此间。",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00038",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "请坐！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00039",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "有坐。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00040",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "请问小娘子，适才有一位打虎的壮士，是你的什么人吓？",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00041",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "是我的舍弟。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00042",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "令弟。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00043",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "舍弟。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00044",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "令弟。吓，哈哈哈！请问适才有一年老的妈妈，是你的什么人？",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00045",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "那是家母。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00046",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "令堂。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00047",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "家母。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00048",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "令堂。吓，哈哈哈！请问小娘子，你的尊字贵表？",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00049",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "我叫桂娟。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00050",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "哦。你叫桂娟。你这“桂”，乃是“月中丹桂”之“桂”；但不知你那“娟”呢？",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00051",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "就是那“月内婵娟”之“娟”。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00052",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "哦。那“月内婵娟”之“娟”。非是学生说，你倒占了一个好美的名儿。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00053",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "笑",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "吓，哈哈哈！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00054",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "请问相公尊姓大名？因何到此？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00055",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "学生张子显。我父在朝官拜武陵侯，我是个公子，诺诺，还是个秀才。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00056",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "哦，哎呀，原来是公子秀才到了，奴家不知，多多有罪。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00057",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00058",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "你看！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00059",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "看些什么？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00060",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "看你那个下作的样儿。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00061",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮慢板",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "好一个风流张子显，我爱他青春在少年。站立在书馆用目看，",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00062",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀且住，方才小娘子言道，她叫作什么娟？什么桂？",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00063",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "我叫桂娟呢。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00064",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "口说是桂娟桂娟，非是学生说你，你倒占了一个好美的名儿。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00065",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "笑",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "吓，哈哈！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00066",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮原板",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "他将奴名问一番。有桂娟，言语乱，黑暗里撒下钓鱼竿。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00067",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "哦？",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00068",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "桂娟容颜生得好，倒叫子显喜心间。书馆内引坏我张子显，",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00069",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "桂娟咳嗽。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00070",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "若不然上前拉衣裳。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00071",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "公子礼乐行不正，我母知道送当官。打你板子问你罪，事前容易后悔难！",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00072",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "她不从，也枉然，倒叫子显着了忙。若不然上前去屈膝跪？",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00073",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 73,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "吓，我是公子，又是一个秀才，我岂肯与她下跪？跪不得跪不得。",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00074",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 74,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "桂娟咳嗽。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00075",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 75,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "好吓！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00076",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 76,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "若不然上前去双膝跪，跪跪跪，小娘子念在生可怜！",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00077",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 77,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "吓！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00078",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 78,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "君子做事礼不端，枉戴头巾穿蓝衫。始读诸书知礼义，堂堂的男子无有脸面。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00079",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 79,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "自古道色胆大如天，不怕王法哪怕官。小娘子请过来拜天地，拜定天地了姻缘。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00080",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "老妇上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00081",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "将身来在书馆外，他二人已成了一对姻缘。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00082",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "呀，唗唗！你可是桂娟？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00083",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "儿是桂娟。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00084",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "哪个叫你前来？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00085",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "娘叫儿来。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00086",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "还不与我跪下？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00087",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "跪下就跪下。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00088",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "还不与我起来？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00089",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 89,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "起来就起来。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00090",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 90,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "你可是公子？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00091",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 91,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "是公子。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00092",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 92,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "可是秀才？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00093",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 93,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "是秀才。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00094",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 94,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "好公子！好秀才！哼哼！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00095",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 95,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀且住，闹到这般时候，这年老妈妈是哪里来的？她那里有气，我不免与她赔上一礼，也就完了。吓妈妈，休要动怒，学生这厢有礼。",
      "text_length": 60
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00096",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 96,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "你有礼，老身无礼。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00097",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 97,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "哎！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00098",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 98,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "张嘴吃了老身不成？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00099",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 99,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "我这里与她赔礼，她的气越发大了。小娘子在那里指天画地，莫非叫我与她母亲下上一跪么？吓，我是公子！我是秀才！岂肯与她下跪？哎跪不得，跪不得。哎吓，事到如今，说的什么公子、秀才，我就是他娘的举人、进士，我也要下她一跪，也就完了。吓妈妈，休要动怒，学生这里跪下了。",
      "text_length": 129
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00100",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 100,
      "seq_in_scene": 100,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "你住了罢！方才你说是公子，又是秀才，你与我娘下跪，岂不是想折死我母亲么？",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00101",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 101,
      "seq_in_scene": 101,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "哎吓，一个人在为难之处，你在一旁打搅。你再要打搅……",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00102",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 102,
      "seq_in_scene": 102,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "怎么样？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00103",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 103,
      "seq_in_scene": 103,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "我这一条腿也就跪下了。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00104",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 104,
      "seq_in_scene": 104,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "桂娟"
      ],
      "text": "我这里奉陪。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00105",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 105,
      "seq_in_scene": 105,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "你们来看，他们油盐酱醋，合了味了。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00106",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 106,
      "seq_in_scene": 106,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "他二人见了面双膝下跪，倒叫我大张口无有话言。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00107",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 107,
      "seq_in_scene": 107,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "先前提亲为何不允？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00108",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 108,
      "seq_in_scene": 108,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "山遥路远，拿礼不便。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00109",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 109,
      "seq_in_scene": 109,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "不用财礼，对着老身一拜。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00110",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 110,
      "seq_in_scene": 110,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "多谢妈妈！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00111",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 111,
      "seq_in_scene": 111,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "张子显"
      ],
      "text": "多谢妈妈许姻缘，子显才把心放宽。小娘子请过来拜天地，拜完了天地了姻缘。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00112",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 112,
      "seq_in_scene": 112,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "老妇"
      ],
      "text": "哽！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01011016_e00113",
      "play_id": "01011016",
      "scene_id": "01011016_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 113,
      "seq_in_scene": 113,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张子显、桂娟、老妇同下。",
      "text_length": 12
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}